Mushy could not belive is eyes! There was a baby Bloop! Swimming happily around in shallow water. 
Regretting that he forgot his camera, Mushy takes a moment to capture a mental picture of the scene before him.
The beauty of the lake, the mountainous landscape behind it, and Bloop slipping above and below the surface of the water.
Satisfied with his discovery, he heads back home to work on a sketch and the story of how he found the lake squishy of Lake moj moj .
